    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it seriously still has that new car smell and the paint is literally flawless! I've babied this thing since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
