    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen of analog performance. This vehicle features a high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and variable valve timing, mated to a precise six-speed close-ratio manual transmission. The longitudinal drivetrain delivers power through a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is impeccably preserved, retaining factory-spec torsional rigidity with a suspension geometry utilizing gas-pressurized dampers and stiffened anti-roll bars. The braking system employs ventilated rotors and multi-piston calipers for superior thermal management. Finished in its original concours-level paint with a flawless interior, this car represents a rare opportunity for the collector seeking mechanical perfection and a documented service pedigree.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
